data.description: Solid 4-family building located off the Delmar Loop, offered at a price to create a solid potential cap rate. Great location for Washington University students/grad students as well. Each unit has 5 rooms, 1 bedroom, 1 bath.  Current tenants are month to month and is potentially under rented.3 units currently occupied and one vacant unit where owner has started updates. VA loan is potentially assumable at 3%. New roof (coming soon)…Building also has newer water heaters, some newer furnaces, updated electric, basement has storage lockers for tenants, Off street parking lot behind building. Great location, short walk to Delmar Loop, BB Hill, restaurants, movies, arts, entertainment, bodega, shopping and also close to Washington University. Great for Investor or Owner Occupant. Schedule your appointment today!
